<chapter xml:id="ch09-open-quantum-systems-dimension-6-" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Open Quantum Systems (Dimension 6)</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>This chapter explores a crucial dimension of the quantum framework. Covers systems coupled to environments, master equations, decoherence mechanisms, transition from quantum to classical behavior.</p>
  </introduction>
  <section><title>Overview</title>
    <p>This chapter continues development of the 11-dimensional quantum framework. Key concepts and applications are developed systematically.</p>
  </section>
  <section><title>Core Content</title>
    <p>Detailed treatment of major topics and techniques for this domain of quantum mechanics.</p>
  </section>
